In this folder you can find the DoNOF manual in PDF format (https://donof-documentation.readthedocs.io/, https://donof.readthedocs.io/).

The current input-reference source is:

- `namelist.md`: up-to-date Markdown reference for `&INPRUN`, `&NOFINP`, and `&INPDYN`

Distribution copies are:

- `namelist.pdf`: PDF version of the input reference
